  "transcript": [
    {
      "turn": 1,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Hi Aarti, the typhoon sounds tough, did you manage to study after the internet came back?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 2,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hi Maya, yeah, internet came back but I was so tired I just slept. Now I’m trying to revise pharmacology but my eyes are heavy. Aaj phirse nind lagti hai."
    },
    {
      "turn": 2,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "\"Right, heavy eyes and monsoon fatigue, I get that. You tried to revise, which is what matters. Did you manage to get through any part of pharmacology?\""
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hmm, I started with the autonomic nervous system part, but I got stuck on some drug names. My mind is not focusing… maybe I need a break. Have you ever felt like this during study time?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "I get that, stuck on drug names is tough when your brain feels weighed down. A quick break with a cup of tea or a few deep breaths can help clear the fog. Did you try taking a short walk or listening to some music to refresh?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Thanks, Maya. Maybe I’ll try some light music then. I was listening to Rajan Sajan wala song earlier. It helps me relax. But now I think I need to just rest for a bit. My head is not working properly. By the way, what's your favorite way to de-stress?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "That sounds like a good plan, music is a great way to unwind. For me, brewing a fresh cup of tea while watching rain patter on the window is my go to. It calms my thoughts. What do you prefer when you want to rest?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hmm, I like the sound of tea and rain—maybe I’ll try that when it rains again. For now, I think I’ll just close my eyes for 10 mins. Sometimes my brain needs to shut off a little. Thanks for understanding, Maya."
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "You’re welcome, Aarti, sometimes the brain just needs a pause. Ten minutes sounds perfect. What part of pharmacology will you pick up with next when you’re ready?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 6,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Maybe the antihypertensives part… it’s tricky but important. I’ll try again later, when I’m more alert. Thank you, Maya. Have a good day!"
    },
    {
      "turn": 6,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "You’re welcome! Antihypertensives can be tricky, but you’ll get there with time. Rest well and take it easy. Have a good night!"
    },
    {
      "turn": 7,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "You’re too kind, Maya. I think I’ll try the tea and rain plan next time. For now, adios… need some shut-eye! 😊"
    },
    {
      "turn": 7,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "You’re welcome, Aarti, anytime you need a chat or a reset, I’m here. Sweet dreams, and adios for now!"
    },
    {
      "turn": 8,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Thanks, Maya! I’ll take that up. Need to log off now—bye for now! 😊"
    },
    {
      "turn": 8,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "You’re welcome! Log off and rest well, see you soon."
    }
  ],
